                  "pageTitle": "Bane of Infested",
                  "pageId": 116459,
                  "revisionId": 2687236,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "For example, if you had a Riven Mod with x0.5 Damage to Infested and a max rank Bane of Infested with x1.3 Damage to Infested, you would have a 1 - 0.5 + 0.3 = x0.8 multiplier for damage against Infested with both mods equipped."
